<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="depress-vt">depress <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'pres/    美 /dɪ'pres/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>将 (某物) 压下；推下；拉下：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>depress a button 
按按钮</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>使抑郁；使沮丧；使消沉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Raining weather always depresses me. 
雨天常让我感到压抑。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>使萧条；削弱：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Several factors combined to depress the housing market. 
几个因素加在一起令房地产市场低迷。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>depressed /dɪ'prest/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t get <strong>depressed about</strong> the spilt milk. 
覆水难收，不要因此沮丧。</p></div>

<p>depressing /dɪ'presɪŋ/ adj   </p></div>